                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9284" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0302</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">869 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以义促航，以行固义——东航ESG传播 高质量 “航行”轨迹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Promoting Navigation with Righteousness and Solidifying Righteousness with Action——China Eastern Airlines ESG Spreads High Quality &quot;Navigation&quot; Track</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王颖晖，张晔，廖茂君，权钺</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东航技术应用研发中心有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；ESG 传播；高质量发展；国产大飞机；绿色飞行</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG, ESG communication, High-quality development, Domestic large aircraft, Green flight</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG是目前全球企业管理和金融投资领域高度重视的发展理念，该理念强调经营管理行为不应该只追求财务绩效，还要关注生态环境保护、社会责任履行和公司治理，与中国经济“高质量发展”这一主题高度契合，其内容体系也为企业践行高质量发展提供必要的工具。同时ESG可帮助中国企业以绿色可持续的高标准面向世界，投入国际大循环，实现高质量的“走出去”。案例描述了中国东方航空公司一系列有特色、有温度、有成效的企业履责行为，从绿色航空、低碳飞行、乡村振兴、社区关怀、服务创新等方面投映出ESG理念下中国央企的可持续发展行动。案例旨在引导学生认识ESG是中国经济社会实现高质量发展、全面绿色转型的重要抓手，培育企业的ESG意识；学习ESG传播的可持续发展内涵与途径、方法；体会央企在传播“中国好故事”的ESG实践中展示出“发出中国声音”的制度自信与责任担当；感悟在中国特色的ESG框架中应该如何讲好中国“好故事”，推动各地区的可持续发展，促进经济和社会的包容性增长，以实现全体人民共同富裕和幸福。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">ESG is a highly valued development concept in the field of global enterprise management and financial investment. This concept emphasizes that business management behavior should not only pursue financial performance but also focus on ecological environment protection, fulfilling social responsibilities, and improving governance levels. It aligns closely with the theme of &quot;high-quality development&quot; in the Chinese economy, and its content system also provides necessary tools for enterprises to practice high-quality development. ESG can promote domestic enterprises to adhere to higher standards, integrate into international circulation, and achieve a high-level &quot;going out&quot;. This case describes a series of distinctive, warm, and effective corporate responsibility behaviors by China Eastern Airlines, reflecting the sustainable development actions of Chinese state-owned enterprises under the ESG concept. These include green aviation, low-carbon flight, rural revitalization, community care, and service innovation. The case aims to guide students to understand that ESG is an important lever for achieving high-quality development and comprehensive green transformation of China&#39;s economy and society. It also seeks to cultivate ESG awareness among enterprises; Learn the sustainable development connotations, approaches, and methods of ESG communication; Experience the institutional confidence and sense of responsibility in spreading the &quot;China&#39;s Good Stories&quot; by Chinese central State-owned enterprises who Implement ESG practice of &quot;delivering voice of China&quot;; Understand how to tell China&#39;s &quot;good story&quot; well in the ESG framework with Chinese characteristics, promote sustainable development in various regions, promote inclusive economic and social growth, and achieve common prosperity and happiness for all people.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；ESG传播；高质量发展；信号传递理论；中国特色ESG；ESG传播的可持续发展内涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
